    • getRevenueById

      public double getRevenueById(String carId)
      Retrieves the revenue for a specific car ID by summing up all final prices of purchase-type tickets and subtracting the final prices of return-type tickets.
      Parameters:
      carId - The ID of the car for which revenue is calculated.
      Returns:
      The total revenue for the car if found, or -1.0 if no transactions were found.

    • getRevenueByCarType

      Parameters:
      carType - The type of the car for which revenue is calculated.
      Returns:
      The total revenue for the car type if found, or -1.0 if no transactions were found.

    • filterCars

      public void filterCars(String filterOption)
      Filters cars based on a specific condition and displays them. The method supports filtering by 'New', 'Used', or 'Available'.
      Parameters:

    • viewUserTransactions

      public void viewUserTransactions(String username)
      Retrieves and displays all transactions associated with a specific user. Each transaction is printed out; if no transactions are found, a message is displayed.
      Parameters:
      username - The username whose transactions are to be fetched and displayed.
